## 🌐 Supported Languages

The app supports many languages including but not limited to:

| Language   | Code |
|------------|------|
| English    | en   |
| Arabic     | ar   |
| Urdu       | ur   |
| French     | fr   |
| Spanish    | es   |
| German     | de   |
| Chinese    | zh   |
| Hindi      | hi   |
| Japanese   | ja   |
| Portuguese | pt   |

